{"tid":1155233,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！！韓團女成員又屌地板！！！","createTime":"2019-05-14T22:00:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T09:01:49.000Z","uid":237244,"like":85,"dislike":156,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"ae2f323474814625c9aef08a38938bb56d27a031","tid":1155233,"uid":237244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T22:00:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ThE9BURuzyo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FThE9BURuzyo&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgV9mOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=24a73f7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ThE9BURuzyo</a><br />\n趕時間可以飛去3:12<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我係覺得KARD呢隊嘢真係好慘<br />\n想多啲人識佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地係4人混聲組合 兩個女人 兩個男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲歌少有地行歐美風/ 拉丁風<br />\n係韓國既人氣麻麻 係香港更加係冇人識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我真心覺得佢地首首歌都好高質 <br />\n同一般洗腦泡菜歌係完全兩回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開po係真心希望可以有多啲人識佢地 支持佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n條片係佢地係演唱會cover左mi gente首歌仲編埋舞<br />\n唔係想講啲咩 但係lisa又係屌地板<br />\nkard兩個女仔都係屌地板<br />\n真係好傷心人氣爭咁遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9292474e0c40d390fa8ae79ea9bb332183bb4799","tid":1155233,"uid":237244,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T22:02:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2f5e3cf0756b5e439dc1a2c6025d8567adf01580","tid":1155233,"uid":237244,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T22:02:55.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"806e7f13a8bd92898d1d6ef1e2cad5a1aafb91b2","tid":1155233,"uid":237244,"like